# ----- Phase 2: Eval dataset -----
# The IMAGES are large and Mapillary-derived (CC-BY-SA).
# Only the manifest + data.yaml + LABELS are committed so other developers
# can rebuild/verify the same set via scripts/fetch_eval_data.py and
# inherit the project's hand-labels (or auto-labels from
# scripts/prelabel.py — see Phase 6 Plan 06-02). Labels are a few KB
# total, the operator's load-bearing work product, and worth tracking.
data/eval_la/*
!data/eval_la/manifest.json
!data/eval_la/data.yaml
!data/eval_la/.gitkeep
!data/eval_la/labels
!data/eval_la/labels/**

# ----- Phase 3: Mapillary ingest cache -----
# Per-segment image downloads + per-run manifests. Ephemeral by design;
# manifest.json files live under per-segment dirs and are not whitelisted
# (operators can opt to commit specific archived manifests separately).
data/ingest_la/*
!data/ingest_la/.gitkeep
.secrets-local/
